Phase 3b (P3-2) discharge proof for offline_lean.t4 — pure Bool
case-symmetry (`(if b then x else y) == (if ~b then y else x)`).
Closes by case-splitting on b and applying bvEq_refl.

This test is critical for L-16 regression coverage: pre-L-16 the
emitted goal had branches swapped, and the property became
genuinely false. If a future regression re-opens the L-16 swap,
this proof breaks at the `bvEq_refl` step.
